1 shal l provide opportunity to organizations to submit written
2 applications to be received and acted upon by the J.M. Davis
3 Memorial Commission. At the conclusion of the contract, each state
4 agency, nonprofit corporation, individual, or association shall
5 provide the J.M. Davis Memorial Commission with proof of fulfillment
