10 C. Any agreements or contracts providing for the employment of
11 persons or to purchase property or equipment or the construction of
12 any facilities shall not be authorized unless necessary funds have
13 been appropriated by the Legislature or have been otherwise obtained
14 from gifts, grants or contributions actually received by the
15 Commission.
16 SECTION 4. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
